{"type": "article", "id": 27024, "title": "平面变立体的桌椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-19T07:13:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 65, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145406JY7WLCsyupUevcSG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>从墙上取下一张椅子的图片，一番折叠后就变成了一把真正的椅子——这并不是电影中的场景，而是设计师 <a href=\"http://jonghachoi.com/\">Jongha Choi</a> 推出的一个设计项目，名为 De-dimension。这些颜色各异的桌椅都可以从平面变为立体，Choi 希望通过强调这个体验的过程，能让我们对图像有一个崭新的认识，而不是刻板地认为图像只能被限定在一个平面上。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145403jiYho3v8BpndLyTS.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021454044T769fqF5bZm82ip.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145404OzoNM1dF8SRqkH7Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145405griuKtDCkbsHB8LU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145405k4ptLSsyKPh0VJWO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}